STATE
v.
DANGERFIELD. 2018-0033 Supreme Court of Ohio. February 28, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

On motion for leave to file delayed appeal. Motion fails for want of four votes. Cause dismissed.

O'Donnell, Kennedy, and DeGenaro, JJ., would grant the motion for leave. Fischer, J., not participating.
